og.description: ATLANTIC CITY — Executives at AtlantiCare and Geisinger Health System said Thursday that the proposed merger of the two nonprofits will create a united health care system offering affordable and accessible medical services throughout the region.
og.title: AtlantiCare makes case for Geisinger partnership
